txt.en: Barricades can be found at Overwine Hall in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should destroy barricades at Overwine Hall.
Barricades found at Overwine Hall should be destroyed in order weaken the defences of your foes within the Wildwood.
Barricades can be found at Overwine Hall in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should destroy barricades at Overwine Hall.
Foes of the Free Peoples have fortified ruins of Overwine Hall within the Wildwood. Destroying the barricades here should weaken the Overwine Hall defences.
